snippet.title: Johnny Depp The True Victim
snippet.description:
Hey Everyone Welcome Back 
Johnny Depp is the subject matter of this podcast today, this is a very deep subject matter and is a very serious matter of domestic violence that Johnny Depp was a victim of through the hands of his estranged wife Amber Heard. 
We talk about events in 2015, and 2016, leading up to this very messy divorce 
My message that I want everyone to rake away from this is NEN CAN CERTAINLY BE VICTIMS of abuse as well, WOMEN CAN AND certainly do lie about these things and as one I feel I can say with confidence that is a true statement 

I want people to also know that AMBER fully abused the #METOO movement totally 

but for people who ARE true victims of abuse please know that you are not alone and PLEASE talk to someone about this it can help you so much and know that we are here for you in this and if you need to talk to me (Kaitlyn) my DM's on Instagram are always open as well as Sam's we love you all

My Instagram 
https://www.instagram.com/kaitlyn.bono/
My Twitter https://twitter.com/katey1115


US Hotline 
 Domestic Violence Hotline 1-800-799-SAFE (7233)
UK Hotline Phone: 0800 1111 for Childline for children (24-hour helpline)
 
UK Website (NSPCC https://www.nspcc.org.uk/
My Second Channel
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMxw...
 Twitch https://www.twitch.tv/katey1115_

#JohnnyDepp AmberHeard Metoo #JusticeforJohnnyDepp
